## {{DATE}} — Wiki scaffolded via llm-wiki plugin

**Context:** New {{DOMAIN}} wiki initialized.
**Decision:** Use the llm-wiki plugin's default scaffold (10 entity templates, deterministic lint.py, Dataview-driven index).
**Rationale:** Consistent starting point across wikis; plugin updates don't propagate automatically so drift is per-wiki.
